The American professional basketball player, Dwyane Wade, reveals his daughter’s name via his Instagram page. Dwyane and Gabrielle Union, the American actress, welcomed their baby daughter recently. Wade tattoed his daughter’s name, Kaavia James Union Wade, on his shoulders when he was in China.   #TBT Goes back to that one night in China when i decided to get my daughters name tattooed on me. Kaavia James Union Wade! #paternityleave A post shared by  dwyanewade (@dwyanewade) on Nov 15, 2018 at 9:51am PST